Detailed Description

cvmx_mhbw::_err_stat0

These registers count fatal and nonfatal errors (excluding ECC errors in MHBW memories). Note that if multiple HABs have errors in the exact same cycle, only one is counted. Both counters wrap to zero at 2^32.
